标题：福建小吃石花膏，8元一碗，选配40盆料吃！小蜜蜂也都来抢
Fujian's specialty jelly in combination with 40 different types of ingredients! Bees also enjoy it

------

描述：

福建省泉州市特色小吃，四果汤。
"Siguo Tang" ("four fruits soup") is a specialty snack in Quanzhou, Fujian.

主要材料除了各种各样的水果以外，就是石花膏了。
The ingredients are different kinds of fruits, together with "Shihuagao" jelly ("stone flower jelly").

石花膏采用海底天然植物制作而成，看起来莹莹剔透
Shihuagao is made from natural sea plants. The appearance is crystal clear.

搭配水果、蜂蜜来吃的话，解腻消暑
Paired with fruits and honey, it's so refreshing and cooling

很多顾客都会从外地奔过来吃。
Even many customers from other places come here for it.

------

